                ArrayList<Tuple2<String, Integer>> tpLists = new ArrayList<Tuple2<String, Integer>>();
                String[] split = s.split("\\s+");
                for (int i = 0; i <split.length ; i++) {
                    Tuple2 tp = new Tuple2<String,Integer>(split[i], 1);
                    tpLists.add(tp);
                }
                return tpLists.iterator();
            }
        });
```

